snippet.title: Heretic II -  Video Game Trailer (1998, PC Windows)
snippet.description:
Heretic II : official video game trailer.
Developed by Raven Software Corporation
Graphic Engine by id Software
Published by Activision in November 1998 for PC Windows, and in 1999 for PC Linux (ported by Loki Entertainment Software).
A Macintosh version (ported by Contraband Entertainment) was published by MacPlay in 2000.

Year : 1998 (trailer, game).

Trailer found on couvermount CD of french magazine Generation 4 (issue #114, September 1998)
